dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Map shows city or borough and county boundaries; bus routes; national and provincial highways; one way streets; house numbers. Includes two insets maps for map continued, and enlargment of central Dunedin city center. Includes index. "Crown copyright reserved."
